Community

Speakers Series: Nina Totenberg

Sep 25, 2024 | 8:00 pm - 11:00 pm 
 With a career spanning more than 40 years, Totenberg has been at the US Supreme Court longer than any sitting justice. She shares insightful reporting on all aspects of the Court as NPR’s legal affairs correspondent. Her memoir Dinners with Ruth: A Memoir on the Power of Friendships was a New York Times bestseller. READ MORE
